snippet.title: Desert Express (GMTK Game Jam 2021)
snippet.description:
This is our game submission for the Game Maker's Toolkit Game Jam 2021

Embark on a wild ride aboard the Desert Express!
Traverse a hostile desert and defend your train against the local entities.
You can unhook from the train, but watch out not to run out of energy!
Need some more firepower? Hook up to the front carriage.
Need to replenish your energy? The second carriage has you covered.
